---
title: "Contacto | Marketing Digital Treasure Coast"
metaDescription: "Contáctanos para marketing digital en Port St. Lucie, Fort Pierce, Stuart y Vero Beach. Consulta gratis por WhatsApp o llama al 772-940-1928. Sin compromiso."
hreflangEs: "/es/contacto/"
hreflangEn: "/en/contact/"
---

<section class="pt-28 pb-16 lg:pb-20" style="background:var(--surf)">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-5">
    <div class="max-w-2xl">
      <span class="accent-line"></span>
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-gray-400 mb-4">Contacto</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl mb-6 leading-tight">Hablemos sobre tu <span style="color:var(--primary)">negocio</span></h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">Sin formularios complicados. Cuéntanos qué necesitas y te respondemos con un plan claro y un presupuesto honesto. Primera consulta gratis.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="py-20 lg:py-28 bg-white">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-5">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-5 gap-10 lg:gap-16">

      <!-- Contact form -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-3">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">Envíanos un mensaje</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-8">Te respondemos en menos de 24 horas en días hábiles.</p>

        <form id="contact-form" class="space-y-5" novalidate>
          <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
            <div>
              <label for="name" class="block text-xs font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-1.5">Nombre *</label>
              <input id="name" name="name" type="text" required autocomplete="name" placeholder="Tu nombre"
                class="w-full rounded-xl border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-sm placeholder-gray-300 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 transition" style="--tw-ring-color:var(--primary)" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <label for="business" class="block text-xs font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-1.5">Negocio</label>
              <input id="business" name="business" type="text" autocomplete="organization" placeholder="Nombre de tu empresa"
                class="w-full rounded-xl border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-sm placeholder-gray-300 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 transition" style="--tw-ring-color:var(--primary)" />
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
            <div>
              <label for="email" class="block text-xs font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-1.5">Email *</label>
              <input id="email" name="email" type="email" required autocomplete="email" placeholder="tucorreo@ejemplo.com"
                class="w-full rounded-xl border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-sm placeholder-gray-300 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 transition" style="--tw-ring-color:var(--primary)" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <label for="phone" class="block text-xs font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-1.5">Teléfono</label>
              <input id="phone" name="phone" type="tel" autocomplete="tel" placeholder="(772) 000-0000"
                class="w-full rounded-xl border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-sm placeholder-gray-300 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 transition" style="--tw-ring-color:var(--primary)" />
            </div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <label for="service" class="block text-xs font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-1.5">¿Qué servicio te interesa?</label>
            <select id="service" name="service"
              class="w-full rounded-xl border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-gray-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 transition bg-white" style="--tw-ring-color:var(--primary)">
              <option value="">Selecciona una opción</option>
              <option value="gbp">Google Business Profile</option>
              <option value="meta-ads">Meta Ads (Facebook/Instagram)</option>
              <option value="google-ads">Google Ads</option>
              <option value="web">Diseño web</option>
              <option value="branding">Branding y logotipo</option>
              <option value="social">Redes sociales</option>
              <option value="print">Materiales impresos</option>
              <option value="package">Paquete completo</option>
              <option value="other">Otro / No sé aún</option>
            </select>
          </div>

          <div>
            <label for="message" class="block text-xs font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-1.5">Mensaje *</label>
            <textarea id="message" name="message" required rows="5" placeholder="Cuéntanos brevemente sobre tu negocio y lo que quieres lograr..."
              class="w-full rounded-xl border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-sm placeholder-gray-300 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 transition resize-none" style="--tw-ring-color:var(--primary)"></textarea>
          </div>

          <div id="form-msg" class="hidden text-sm font-medium px-4 py-3 rounded-xl"></div>

          <button type="submit"
            class="w-full sm:w-auto inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-xl px-8 py-3.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity"
            style="background:var(--primary)">
            Enviar mensaje →
          </button>
        </form>
      </div>

      <!-- Contact info sidebar -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-2 space-y-6">

        <div class="contact-card reveal rounded-2xl p-6">
          <div class="icon-wrap mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" style="color:var(--primary)" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">WhatsApp — más rápido</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-4">La forma más rápida de contactarnos. Te respondemos directamente.</p>
          <a href="{{ site.whatsapp }}?text=Hola%2C%20me%20gustar%C3%ADa%20una%20consulta%20sobre%20marketing%20digital%20para%20mi%20negocio."
             target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
             class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity"
             style="background:#25D366">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347z"/><path d="M12.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413A11.824 11.824 0 0012.05 0zm0 21.785h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.861 9.861 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884z"/></svg>
            Escribir por WhatsApp
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-card reveal rounded-2xl p-6" style="transition-delay:.07s">
          <div class="icon-wrap mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" style="color:var(--primary)" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">Llámanos</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-3">Lunes a viernes, 9 am – 6 pm (ET)</p>
          <a href="tel:{{ site.phoneRaw }}" class="text-lg font-semibold hover:underline" style="color:var(--primary)">{{ site.phone }}</a>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-card reveal rounded-2xl p-6" style="transition-delay:.14s">
          <div class="icon-wrap mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" style="color:var(--primary)" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">Email</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-3">Respondemos en menos de 24 h</p>
          <a href="mailto:{{ site.email }}" class="text-sm font-semibold hover:underline break-all" style="color:var(--primary)">{{ site.email }}</a>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-card reveal rounded-2xl p-6" style="transition-delay:.21s">
          <div class="icon-wrap mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" style="color:var(--primary)" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">Área de servicio</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">Atendemos negocios en <strong>Port St. Lucie, Fort Pierce, Stuart y Vero Beach</strong> — Treasure Coast, Florida.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FAQ quick -->
<section class="py-20 lg:py-24" style="background:var(--surf)">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-5">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-10 text-center">Preguntas frecuentes</h2>
    <div class="space-y-5">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 p-6">
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">¿Cuánto cuesta una consulta?</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">La primera consulta es completamente gratis y sin compromiso. Te presentamos un diagnóstico y una propuesta clara antes de que decidas nada.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 p-6">
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">¿Trabajan con cualquier tipo de negocio?</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Sí — restaurantes, salones, clínicas, contratistas, tiendas, servicios profesionales y más. Si tienes clientes locales en el Treasure Coast, podemos ayudarte.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 p-6">
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">¿En cuánto tiempo veo resultados?</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Depende del servicio: Google Business Profile puede mejorar en semanas; los anuncios de pago generan tráfico desde el primer día; el posicionamiento orgánico tarda 3–6 meses. Siempre te diremos qué esperar y cuándo.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
